# 5. Slot Reconciliation Algorithm (Critical)

The **slot reconciler** ensures safe updates without destroying slots.

File:

```
server/app/services/calendar_sync/slot_reconciler.rb
```

---

## Reconciliation Flow

```
BEGIN TRANSACTION

booking.lock!

existing_slots =
booking.availability_slots.lock.reload

expected_slots =
generate from booking dates

existing_map = slots keyed by datetime
expected_map = expected keyed by datetime

to_create = expected - existing
to_delete = existing - expected
```

---

## Insert Missing Slots

```
AvailabilitySlot.insert_all(
  attrs,
  unique_by: index_availability_slots_unique
)
```

---

## Delete Extra Slots

```
booking.availability_slots
.where(id: ids_to_delete)
.delete_all
```

---

## Safety Guarantees

The reconciler must guarantee:

```
Never delete all slots
Never recreate identical slots
Ignore duplicate insert conflicts
Remain idempotent
```

---

## Concurrency Protection

Inside reconciler:

```
booking.lock!
booking.availability_slots.lock.reload
```

Protects against:

```
admin approval
user booking
background sync
```

