# 10. Background Worker

File:

```
server/app/jobs/calendar_sync_job.rb
```

Runs every:

```
15 minutes
```

Select:

```
50 homestays per run
```

Workers:

```
max 10 concurrent
```

Each executes:

```
CalendarSync::SyncHomestay.call(homestay)
```

---

# 11. Sync Health Monitoring

On success:

```
last_calendar_sync_at = now
last_calendar_sync_success_at = now
sync_error_count = 0
last_calendar_sync_error = nil
```

On failure:

```
sync_error_count += 1
last_calendar_sync_error = message
```

If:

```
sync_error_count >= 5
```

Then:

```
calendar_sync_enabled = false
```

